WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([Content], [Description], [DisplayOrder], [GroupAlias], [Image], [Name], [Status], [Url])
VALUES (i.[Content], i.[Description], i.[DisplayOrder], i.[GroupAlias], i.[Image], i.[Name], i.[Status], i.[Url])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted38;

SELECT [t].[Id] FROM [Slides] t
INNER JOIN @inserted38 i ON ([t].[Id] = [i].[Id])
ORDER BY [i].[_Position];
